Problems  

1. sliderInput("aveloading_cross", "Average Cross Loading (CL)": the maximum value sometimes is less than the minimum value 
  e.g., when # of variable = 8, factor corrlation in the true model = .2, ML = .48, MR = .65, CL = .79, CR = 0

  Suggested change 
    output$slidemax_cross <- renderUI({
      sliderInput("aveloading_cross", "Average Cross Loading (CL)", min = 0, 
                  max = max(round((sqrt(1-(input$aveloading)^2+(input$fcor*input$aveloading)^2)-input$fcor*input$aveloading),2),0), 
                  value = 0) 
    })